Numerele introduse sunt:
<p></p>
x= <script> x=2,y=2; document.write(x)</script>
<p></p>
y= <script>document.write(y)</script>
<p></p>
Suma celor 2 numere este: <script>var a=x+y; document.write(a)</script><p></p>
Diferenta celor 2 numere este: <script>var b=x-y; document.write(b)</script><p></p>
Produsul celor 2 numere este: <script>var c=x*y; document.write(c)</script><p></p>
Raportul celor 2 numere este: <script>var d=x/y; document.write(d)</script><p></p>
